 culture, grand humaniste et habile littérateur, Bertrand Savoie a su nous laisser ce brillant document posthume, témoignage exemplaire d’un être dédié à la profession médicale. Extrait de la préface  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aPhysicians (General practice)zQuébec (Province)vBiography. 0aPhysicians (General practice). 0aPhysicianszQuébec (Province)vBiography. 0aPhysicians. 7aHEALTH & FITNESS / General.2bisacsh1 aHould, Fernand J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSavoie, Jean-Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2015z978311127402708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2015z978311127703540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276372566640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763725666423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763725666/original  a978-3-11-127402-7  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-127703-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2015b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles